Interface DataObject

    public interface DataObject
extends Layered, eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.generator.modeling.common.nodes.NodeMetadata
    An interface for accessing any data object that is modeled in some DataModel. It may be either CompositeDataObject or SimpleDataObject that also extend this interface.
